+---------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: Float64(100) * CAST(sum(CASE WHEN tpch.tpch.part.p_type LIKE Utf8("PROMO%") THEN tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount ELSE Int64(0) END) AS Float64) / CAST(sum(tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount) AS Float64) AS promo_revenue                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |   Aggregate: groupBy=[[]], aggr=[[sum(CASE WHEN tpch.tpch.part.p_type LIKE Utf8("PROMO%") THEN __common_expr_1 ELSE Decimal128(Some(0),38,4) END) AS sum(CASE WHEN tpch.tpch.part.p_type LIKE Utf8("PROMO%") THEN tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount ELSE Int64(0) END), sum(__common_expr_1) AS sum(tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * Int64(1) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount)]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |     Projection: tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice * (Decimal128(Some(1),20,0) - tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount) AS __common_expr_1, tpch.tpch.part.p_type                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |       Inner Join: tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_partkey = tpch.tpch.part.p_partkey                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |
|               |         Projection: tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_partkey, tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_extendedprice, tpch.tpch.lineitem.l_discount                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
